dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Dept. of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Inside of brochure features road map of the Lebanon State Forest (now Brendan T. Byrne State Forest) and surrounding areas, including New Lisbon and Whiting. Portions of tracks on the Pennsylvania and Central Railroad of New Jersey lines are visible. In corner is a guide to the Deep Hollow Pond picnic and camp sites. Legend indicates state forest, streams, forest office, fire tower and restricted camp sites. Alongside main map is a smaller map called Pictoral Guide to Pakim Pond Recreational Area.
